    <description><![CDATA[
# Zone New Companion

**Unified desktop IPTV companion app for Xtream Codes, Stalker Portal, and M3U playlists**

## Features

- **Multiple Portal Support**: Connect to Xtream Codes, Stalker Portal, or M3U playlists
- **Modern UI**: Clean PyQt6 interface with dark theme support
- **VLC Integration**: Seamless streaming through VLC media player
- **EPG Support**: Electronic Program Guide for live TV
- **Series Support**: Browse and play TV series with season/episode navigation
- **History**: Quick reconnect to previous portals
- **Verification**: Built-in stream verification tools

## Requirements

- VLC media player must be installed separately
- Windows 10/11

## Installation

```powershell
choco install zone-new-companion
```

## Usage

1. Launch Zone New Companion from the Start Menu
2. Enter your portal credentials (URL, MAC, username/password)
3. Click Connect and browse channels
4. Double-click any channel to play in VLC

## Links

- [GitHub Repository](https://github.com/kidpoleon/zone-new-companion)
